title: Region transfer missing
body: I'm in the "Account" section in the store and the only thing I see is "Summoner Name Change". Am I the only one not getting the transfer options? (EUNE, want to transfer to EUW soon)

replies.body: Transfers are down right while we prep for season rewards.  Per our [announcement](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/news/game-updates/features/account-transfers-going-cooldown), we expect to have it back up in November.

Just signed up, wrong region accidently.
Would also like to switch region to EUW.
Hey! It's already January and they are still down. Please reply so I know when I can change again. Thanks.
